<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>rén shēng zhī lù shàng 迦南946</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 rén shēng zhī lù shàng, nǐ liú xià shén me? shān suī wú yán shuǐ suī wú yǔ, xiǎo lù dōu jì dé.
 rén shēng zhī lù shàng yào shēn shēn sī suǒ. zuì dà zuì dà de ān wèi shì yé sū péi bàn zhe.
 dài rén yào yǒu ēn, zhǔ zhè yàng jiào dǎo wǒ. chéng shí cí ài xǐ lè, qín jiǎn guò shēng huó.
 jìng wèi yé hé huá, yī shēng wèi zhì bǎo. nǐ hòu yì yǔ nǐ hòu yì zhī hòu yì yǒng zài fú zhōng guò.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>946</hymn_number>
</song>